ЁFreddie Gray (Junior)

7th May 1950 - 10th December 2016

You were our hardest goodbye.

Sometimes, happy memories hurt the most.

We love you. we miss you, we grieve for you. and so,
we will live our lives to make you proud of us.

Love You Dad x Love You Grandad x Love You Son x Love You Freddie x

Miss You Always.


Richard Thomas Gray (Richi)

15th August 1975 - 16th August 2017

You left without warning. Gone so fast.
Now all we have are memories of our past.

You were loved by so many, you might not have known,
but in our hearts is where you have grown.

Miss You Always & Forever. Love Your Mum, Your Sis Shell &
Your Beautiful Daughter Caitlin.

"Love You Lots Like Jelly Tots""╦
