ЧThis bench is dedicated to the memory of
Dorothy ("Dot") Anthony Flanagan
1931 - 2017
"We're blessed", she used to say when sitting
on the prom looking out at sea. And how right
she was, though it was us - her daughter and
grandchildren - who were blessed since Dot was a
great mother to Joan and more like a grand mother
than grandmother to Kirsty and Lee.
